title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You are a powerful catalyst for change now, yet you are transformed, in turn, by the interactions you initiate. People expect you to lead the charge for adventure and to present fascinating topics for discussion today. Fortunately, you may already be organizing a memorable getaway for friends. Or, you might be making plans to see an artists exhibition or a concert performance. In any event, keep things simple by sparking an interesting exchange about whats special to you in the world. You dont necessarily need to sway anyones mind one particular way or another. Your passion is an irresistible force. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
